</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/unwirelife/~4/B-Cirq4pS5A" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>]]></content:encoded><feedburner:origLink>https://unwire.hk/2021/09/24/apple-epic-fortnite-appstore/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=apple-epic-fortnite-appstore</feedburner:origLink></item><item><title>Switch Online 加入 Mega Drive、N64 遊戲，推出無線版復刻主機手掣</title><link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/unwirelife/~3/Hq3cZ2oEsso/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[牙 Step]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Fri, 24 Sep 2021 08:26:03 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[遊戲情報]]></category><category><![CDATA[Mega Drive]]></category><category><![CDATA[Nintendo]]></category><category><![CDATA[Nintendo 64]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1062192</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>Nintendo 任天堂在 9 月 24 日上午的「Nintendo Direct 2021.9.24」直播活 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Nintendo 任天堂在 9 月 24 日上午的「Nintendo Direct 2021.9.24」直播活動中，宣布 Nintendo Switch Online 將在 10 月下旬推出「Nintendo Switch Online + 擴充包」服務計劃。會員購買新方案將能夠遊玩 Nintendo 64 和 Mega Drive 的懷舊遊戲，並復刻兩款主機的經典手掣。</p><p>購買了新方案的會員在 10 月可以遊玩 8 款高清版 Nintendo 64 的初代 3D 遊戲，並支持最多同時 4 人線上或線下對戰。日後還會新增《薩爾達傳說，魔吉拉的面具》、《瑪利歐高爾夫 64》和《星之卡比 64》等遊戲。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1062201" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/3-1-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/3-1-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/3-1-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/3-1.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1062202" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/2-1-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/2-1-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/2-1-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/2-1.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>新方案亦同時上架以下 14 款高清版 Mega Drive 遊戲，日後亦會陸續更新遊戲庫。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1062203" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/4-6-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/4-6-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/4-6-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/4-6.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1062204" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/4-1-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/4-1-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/4-1-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/4-1.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>與此同時，為了配合 Nintendo 64 和 Mega Drive 的懷舊遊戲體驗，任天堂將復刻 「Nintendo 64 控制器」和「SEGA Mega Drive Fighting Pad 6B」兩款手掣，並提供無線遊玩功能。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1062210" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/5-1-580x580.jpeg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/5-1-580x580.jpeg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/5-1-120x120.jpeg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/5-1.jpeg 720w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ 「Nintendo 64 控制器」。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1062212" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/5-3-580x580.jpeg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/5-3-580x580.jpeg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/5-3-120x120.jpeg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/5-3.jpeg 720w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ 「SEGA Mega Drive Fighting Pad 6B」。</p><p class="p1">資料來源：<a href="https://www.nintendo.com.hk/topics/article/a_210924_07.html">Nintendo</a></p>
