re0005-5-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0005-5-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0005-5.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>就現場所見，大量放機者於旺角先達商場內的回收售賣長龍放售其「戰利品」，每間鋪都有十幾廿人排隊爭住放 iPhone。由後生至到上年紀的炒家都有。大部份人都拿著多於一部 iPhone 前往放售。現場亦有不少人前往問價，但只有好價的幾間店鋪有人龍出現。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0000-9.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1062265" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0000-9-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0000-9-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0000-9-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0000-9-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0000-9.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0001-7.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1062266" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0001-7-590x580.jpg" alt="" width="590" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0001-7-590x580.jpg 590w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0001-7-915x900.jpg 915w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0001-7-768x755.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0001-7.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 590px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0005-5.jpg"><br /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0006-2.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1062273" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0006-2-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0006-2-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0006-2-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0006-2-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0006-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>每部最多獲利 $1500</h2><p>回收價方面，炒機者獲利最高為 iPhone 13 Pro Max 1TB，回收價達 $15,100，比原價 HK$13,599 多 HK$1,501（大吉利是）。預期最多買家們想入手的 256GB 以及 512GB 機種，其售價分別為 256GB 的 HK$11300（官價$10,199，獲利$1,101）以及 HK$13,100（官價$11,899，獲利$1,201）。</p><h2>官方有現貨 iPhone 13 Pro 都有得炒</h2><p>就連官方有現貨供應的 iPhone 13 Pro 系列都有得炒，現場資料所示，其回收價為 iPhone 13 Pro 128GB 的 HK$9000，以及 256GB 的 HK$9900，對比官方現價都有 HK$501 以及 HK$601 的差價。反而更高容量的機種就似乎不設回收。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0003-6.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1062269" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0003-6-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0003-6-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0003-6-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0003-6-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/unwire0003-6.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>先達某回收價較高店之 iPhone 13 Pro 系列回收價（24/9 中午現場消息）</p><table style="width: 44.375515210341646%;" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tbody><tr><td style="width: 48.23848238482385%;" valign="top"></td><td style="width: 12.737127371273713%;" valign="top">黑</td><td style="width: 12.737127371273713%;" valign="top">白</td><td style="width: 12.737127371273713%;" valign="top">金</td><td style="width: 76.89180737961226%;" valign="top">藍</td></tr><tr><td style="width: 48.23848238482385%;" valign="top">iPhone 13 Pro Max 